INSERT INTO tutor_profiles (userId, bio, qualifications, subjects, gradeLevels, hourlyRate, yearsOfExperience, approvalStatus, isActive)
SELECT id, 
  'Experienced educator passionate about student success',
  'Professional teaching credentials and subject matter expertise',
  '["Mathematics","Science"]',
  '["High School","College"]',
  50.00,
  5,
  'pending',
  true
FROM users 
WHERE email IN ('maya.b@edkonnect.com', 'shriti.s@edkonnect.com')
AND id NOT IN (SELECT userId FROM tutor_profiles);
